TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo provide the content of the file ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
